            </div>

            <div class="p-4 rounded-lg mb-6" style="background: rgba(47, 214, 200, 0.05);">
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: var(--bc-primary-blue);">Perfect for:</p>
              <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--bc-dark-gray);">Remote workforce assessment, initial screening, at-scale testing</p>
