                  </svg>
                  <span style="color: var(--bc-dark-gray);">Evaluates English in professional, academic, and social situations</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--bc-cta-pink);" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
